'''''Wonderstruck''''' is a [[Canadian]] [[educational]] [[television series]] which taught [[science]] to children, that aired on the [[Canadian Broadcasting Corporation|CBC]] between 1986 and 1992. It was hosted by [[Bob McDonald (journalist)|Bob McDonald]].  Every episode began with McDonald saying ''I'm curious about things.  Why they are the way they are, and why they're not something else.''

